summary: Ya know what’s weird? When I originally heard of Aggretsuko, the characters, and the ships and stuff never registered with me....
body:
Ya know what’s weird? When I originally heard of Aggretsuko, the characters, and the ships and stuff never registered with me. The only thing that got me at first was the mention of metal. The character singing death metal (well, an interpretation of death metal, it’s really more thrash than anything) was pretty interesting, but I totally forgot about it. Then the thing that got me into the show was, of all things, Retsuaida. I came for the death metal, I stayed for the ship.

I’m not even into death metal necessarily! I’m a power metal fan, usually. :P

summary: Aggretsuko: A Day in the Life of Retsuko Sentence Starters
title: Aggretsuko: A Day in the Life of Retsuko Sentence Starters
body:
Feel free to change pronouns or restructure sentences as needed.

“My name is ____.”

“My brand new life starts today!”

“New places, new people to meet… There’s a bright future ahead of me, filled with hopes and dreams!”

“I don’t wanna go to work.”

“I’ll count to ten. After that I’ll be… a model citizen.”

“This can’t be happening.”

“I’ll just do this weird dance to keep them looking up.”

“Good morning, [name]!”

“It made me think you’re really a kind and wonderful person!”

“Hey, did you hear the rumor?”

“It’s morning and I’m tired already.”

“I hate that girl. I’m following her online, though.”

“She posts a thigh pic once every thirteen days, without fail.”

“This is basically hot water.”

“It’s cute, isn’t it?”

“Looking at your face just makes me sick!”

“How can any person be such a dick!?”

“[Name], you kiss up a lot.”

“I’m gonna get a drink.”

“I have a bit of a favor to ask…”

“Well, should we head back?”

“But I have a secret that no one can know about.”
